Come on if your offhand is 30% of your dmg you would gain between 1% and 8% increase in dmg in a manner that is utterly inconsistant with verants design.  Look at the ranger haste cloak from sky that was recently changed to only be usable while being worn.<br>
<br>
Now be happy you get to proc a lvl 60 shaman buff rather than bitching about having to actually wield the weapon that procs it.<br>
